name: WED-1016 'Techie' Droid
Lore: 'Cybot Galactica starship maintenance droid. Repairs over 5,000 different onboard systems. Used by Rebel Alliance salvage teams.',
Text: 'While at an exterior planet site or docking bay, once per turn may lose 1 Force to place a ''hit'' starship or vehicle at same site, adjacent site, related system or related cloud sector in Used Pile instead of Lost Pile.',
